description: Michael Hashim remembers encounters with saxophonist Pony Poindexter, trombonist Benny Morton, as well as jazz clubs Eddie Condon's and Jimmy Ryan's, with memories of Red Balaban, Jo Jones, Bobby Pratt, Tony Bennett, Joe Muranyi, Artie Baker, Roy Eldridge, Scott Hamilton, Lou Donaldson, Freddie Freeloader, and others.  Recorded by Michael Steinman for JAZZ LIVES (http://www.jazzlives.wordpress.com).
